WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Schools of fish create amazing mathematical patterns!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Fish swim together in groups for protection and efficiency.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
We can count groups, estimate quantities, and spot patterns.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Different fish species form schools of different sizes.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Let's explore the maths behind these underwater communities!